ActIndian Act
SubjectAdministration and Control of Reserve Land Willow Cree Indian Reserve, Saskatchewan ** Transfer **
PrecisOrder (1) consenting to the exercise of the power of Saskatchewan to take a portion of land in Willow Cree Indian Reserve, Saskatchewan, pursuant to subsection 35(1) of the Indian Act; and (2) authorizing, in lieu of such taking, the transfer of administration and control of the required lands, pursuant to subsection 35(3) of the Indian Act.
